{"tid":2080244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"過半非民主派受訪者認同高官親屬應放棄外國國籍 以表「效忠」","createTime":"2020-06-26T09:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T11:59:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"502414479d1ce9ee73b6a6758186f7255c30f434","tid":2080244,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所今日（26日）發佈「我們香港人意見群組」的調查結果，題目為「有多支持或反對特首、司長及局長的直系親屬，包括配偶及子女，應該放棄外國國籍以顯示有關官員對中央政府的政治忠誠」...<br />\n<br />\n調查於6月22至24日期間在網上進行，共收回7,147份回應，當中6,208份回應為自稱民主派支持者，700份回應為非民主派支持者，當中包括建制、中間派或無政治傾向人士。結果顯示，民主派支持者中有高達96%人支持特首、司長及局長的直系親屬，包括配偶及子女放棄外國國籍以顯示有關官員對中央政府的政治忠誠，當中93%屬「好支持」；<span style=\"color: red;\">非民主派支持者亦有52%支持，當中42%屬「好支持」</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200626/4ML5BRRDZYOEO3OBQ3N43ESOZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2F4ML5BRRDZYOEO3OBQ3N43ESOZU%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=55adf7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2F4ML5BRRDZYOEO3OBQ3N43ESOZU%2F&h=6929124f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200626/4ML5BRRDZYOEO3OBQ3N43ESOZU/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aade2ccc0a09280e130170227c982f103d9432eb","tid":2080244,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bd41e169df9819b5089fef3c97c5df04319fe6a","tid":2080244,"uid":21470,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴一早係6.9 之前以已經講，依加先出民調有d 遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc5ef90a7663062f1aa116a9f57a014efc87857","tid":2080244,"uid":61207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/